	"description": "Introduction\nOften, when working as web developer, we need to integrate templates. They can\nbe from Photoshop or other software. In this article, we will have a look at the\nbasics of Photoshop for web developers.\n\nThis content was initially written for a workshop for DAMDigital London\n[http://damdigital.com/].\n\nAdobe Photoshop is a raster graphics editor software, meaning it is a program\nthat allows users to create and edit images.\n\nImage source [https://www.adobe.com/products/photoshop.html#her",
